      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs used in validation (RH index, pressure head) must be the same quantities used in the regulatory submission decision.",
      "rationale": "Regulatory decision is based on RH < 1 (relative to predicate). Validation QoIs are identical: RH index derived from volume-averaged scalar stress and exposure time. No surrogate QoIs introduced."
